<h3>Troubleshooting</h3>

<p><strong>Linker errors about Assimp:</strong> Ensure Assimp is installed via Homebrew. Run <code>brew list assimp</code> to verify.</p>

<p><strong>Compilation errors:</strong> Make sure you're using the build script or setting <code>LEAN_CC=/usr/bin/clang</code>. The native code requires a C++17 compatible compiler.</p>
